extends AeBaseFaultMatchingStrategy.AeFaultMatchingRule

Matches if the fault has element data that is a member of a substituion group headed by the element in the catch varaible. Otherwise similar to above AeFaultNameAndData_WSBPEL. This is not a best match rule.
